General Information

Swisse Micellar Makeup Removing Cleansing Water is a natural, gentle, rinse-free makeup remover, formulated to effortlessly remove oil, impurities and stubborn waterproof makeup. Enriched with soothing Cucumber Extract, this cleansing water is fragrance free and non-irritating, leaving your skin feeling clean, soft and hydrated.

Warnings

Test prior to use. In the unlikely event of a negative reaction, consult your medical practitioner.

Ingredients

Water (Aqua) Glycerin (Plant derived) Decyl Glucoside Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Extract Carrageenan Sodium Citrate Citric Acid Dehydroacetic Acid Benzyl Alcohol

Directions

Directions: Soak a cotton pad and gently smooth over eyes and face. Follow with your favourite Swisse cleanser.
